title: 820-3330 Stuck on Apple logo
message:
Hi,

This is a clean board.

How ever P!V5_GPU_S0 was not there. after replacing Q8360 and Q8361 I got 1.35v on this rail and it turned on.

It was working fine with out having any issue but start crashing with audio editing and now half way stuck on apple logo. 
Before it crashed I check ASD OS test and it all passed couple of times. However Internal graphic test graphic were bit scattered.
YOu cant feel much heating on GPU rams or GPU as 2011 boards. As soon it turn on P!V5_GPU_S0 is 1.5v then after chime goes to 1.35v.



Any clue?
